# Path to a local checkout of https://github.com/withakay/glean-docker.
# Recommended: create a symlink at ./.local/glean-docker (repo root) and rely on the compose default.
# If you want to override the default, uncomment and set this to an absolute path.
# GLEAN_DOCKER_PATH=/absolute/path/to/glean-docker

# Optional: override the Glean/Glass image tag used by docker compose.
# Default is "glean-base" (built from ${GLEAN_DOCKER_PATH}/base).
# GLEAN_IMAGE=ghcr.io/withakay/glean-docker/rust:latest

# Optional: override schema directory inside the container.
# Default is /opt/glean/schema/source.
# GLEAN_SCHEMA_DIR=/opt/glean/schema/source

# Optional: workspace path mounted into code-context container at /workspace.
# Default is current repository root.
# WORKSPACE_PATH=.

# Optional: configure embeddings provider.
# EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small

# Optional: enable lexical search with Zoekt.
# ZOEKT_URL=http://zoekt:6070
